<Legal title="Privacy Policy" lastUpdated="March 23, 2026">

  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    SwahiliFlow ("we", "our", "us") is a Swahili language learning app. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name and email address when you sign in with Apple or Google.</li>
    <li><strong>Learning data:</strong> Your roadmap assessment answers, roleplay session transcripts, and progress within the app.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> App interaction patterns such as sessions completed, time spent, and features used.</li>
    <li><strong>Subscription data:</strong> Purchase status and subscription tier (managed by Apple; we do not store payment details).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To provide and personalize your learning experience.</li>
    <li>To generate AI-powered learning plans based on your assessment results.</li>
    <li>To sync your progress across devices.</li>
    <li>To improve the app and develop new features.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Firebase (Google):</strong> Authentication, cloud storage, and real-time data sync.</li>
    <li><strong>Apple Sign In / Google Sign In:</strong> Secure account authentication.</li>
    <li><strong>Apple In-App Purchases:</strong> Subscription management and payment processing.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Each service operates under its own privacy policy.</p>

  <h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
  <p>
    Your data is stored securely using Firebase Cloud Firestore and transmitted over encrypted connections (HTTPS). We take reasonable measures to protect your information but cannot guarantee absolute security.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
  <p>
    We retain your data for as long as your account is active. You may request deletion of your account and associated data by contacting us. Upon request, we will delete your personal data within 30 days.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    SwahiliFlow is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware of such collection, we will delete the information promptly.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
    <li>Request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
    <li>Request deletion of your data.</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent at any time by deleting your account.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected by the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the app constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:
    <br /><a href="mailto:support@swahiliflow.com">support@swahiliflow.com</a>
  </p>

</Legal>
